CHARLATAN
SKIL PROFICIENCIES: Deception, Sleight of Hand
TOOL PROFICIENCIES: Disguise kit, forgery kit
EQUIPMENT:  A set of fine clothes
            a disguise kit
            tools of the con of your choice (ten stopped bottles filled with colored liquid, a set of weighted dice, a deck of marked cards, or a signet ring of an imaginary duke)
